name: opensvm.com
description: Project offers an AI agent on X (twitter previously) which will do on-chain analysis and tell us about the risks and the information related to deployers wallet. It will also help in screening rugs in real time. user can ask the agent about any token and agent will give all the information related to the token including previous transaction history and rug history tied to deployer's wallet. It also offers an upgraded version of Solana explorer with AI assistance.
